  "text": "MassArray. Quantification of DNA methylation was carried out by MALDI-TOF mass spectrometry using EpiTyper by MassArray on bisulfiteconverted DNA, as previously described [CITATION_1] . MassArray primers were designed to cover two regions upstream of the transcription start site of the CDKN2A gene, spanning chr9:21,966,178-21,966,699 and chr9:21,964,659-21,964,922 (primer sequences shown in Supplementary Table S3) .",
